videos.title: Your Doom Has Been Foretold  Much Abrew
videos.description:
Pioneer is missing a real prison deck. Is grinding away opponent's permanent with Doom Foretold as close as we can get to making prison work in the format? Let's find out!

Today's video is brought to you by Card Kingdom. You can pick up some Magic: the Gathering cards (and help support the show) at https://www.cardkingdom.com/mtggoldfish
